=== Noun ===
'''pie''' ([[countable]] and [[uncountable]]; plural: [[pies]])

#A sweet or savoury food item consisting of a [[pastry]] container with a sweet or savour [[filling]], either with or without a pastry [[crust]].
#:''The family had steak and kidney pie for dinner and cherry pie for dessert.''
#Extended to other savoury dishes consisting of meat covered with something other than pastry.
#:''Shepherd's pie is made of mince covered with mashed potato.''

